# Cursor indexing configuration template
# These negation patterns keep important agent/docs files indexable even if
# a repo has broad local ignore rules. If the files are already tracked,
# these lines are harmless belt-and-suspenders.
#
# Copy this file to your project root as `.cursorignore` and customize as needed.

# Useful documentation and agent context
!docs/adr/0001.md
!docs/notes/
!docs/notes/**/*
!docs/entrypoints.md
!docs/plans/
!docs/plans/**/*
!docs/tech-debt.md
!docs/todo-list.md
!docs/context/
!docs/context/**/*
!docs/examples/
!docs/examples/**/*
!docs/ontology_applications/
!docs/ontology_applications/**/*

# Agent instructions / context files
!AGENTS.md

!.cursorignore

# .cursor directory (for cursor-specific configs)
!.cursor/
!.cursor/**/*
